snippet: Spaniard Rafael Nadal will sharpen his grasscourt game at London's Queen's Club ahead of Wimbledon in June, organizers of the Aegon Championships said on Tuesday....
lead_paragraph: Spaniard Rafael Nadal will sharpen his grasscourt game at London's Queen's Club ahead of Wimbledon in June, organizers of the Aegon Championships said on Tuesday.

headline.print_headline: Nadal to Warm Up for Wimbledon at Queen's Club
headline.main: Nadal to Warm Up for Wimbledon at Queen's Club
